OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,FThousands of residents in have been
OL,7,Fwithout heating and hot water for
OL,8,Fdays, after a huge volume of water got
OL,9,Finto gas pipes.
OL,11,FThe major incident was declared in the
OL,12,Fvillages of Ratby and Kirby Muxloe
OL,13,Fafter a water main burst - and with
OL,14,Ftemperatures just above freezing, the
OL,15,Ftiming couldn't have been much worse.
OL,17,FAround 200 gas engineers have
OL,18,Fdescended on the villages from across
OL,19,Fthe country - as villagers rally
OL,20,Ftogether to support the most
OL,21,Fvulnerable in their communities.
