OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,FTimeline of the incident
OL,8,FJust after midday, are 'mobilised' to
OL,9,FRatby and surrounding areas after
OL,10,Fwater reportedly leaked into local gas
OL,11,Fpipes.
OL,13,FEngineers report that there is "a
OL,14,Flarge volume of water in our pipes"
OL,15,Fmeaning some homes and businesses are
OL,16,Fwithout gas.
OL,18,FThe water has to be completely removed
OL,19,Fbefore the gas can be turned back on.
