OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,FCadent said: "the scale of task means
OL,7,Fthis is not going to be a quick
OL,8,Fresolution," adding: "This is going to
OL,9,Ftake some considerable time ` days,
OL,10,Fnot hours."
OL,12,FThey set up a 'customer centre' at
OL,13,FRatby village hall, where local people
OL,14,Fcan pick up a fan heater, blankets,
OL,15,Fand thick socks to keep themselves
OL,16,Fwarm.
OL,18,FEngineers knock on doors in the area
OL,19,Fto safely switch off the gas supply in
OL,20,Faffected homes and businesses.
