OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,FCadent stated that: "We have already
OL,7,Fstarted the preparation work, and
OL,8,Fsince yesterday we have already
OL,9,Fextracted over 30,000 litres of water
OL,10,Ffrom our gas network.
OL,12,F"We don't know how much water has
OL,13,Fentered the network, so we can't say
OL,14,Ffor sure how long it will take to
OL,15,Fclear the network entirely."
OL,17,FThe area is divided into four 'zones'
OL,18,Ffor the engineers to work across.
OL,19,F'Warm Welcome' sites are set up across
OL,20,Fthe area to help locals stay warm
OL,21,Fwhilst their homes are without gas.
