OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,FEngineers continue to urge people not
OL,7,Fto try and turn off their gas supply
OL,8,Fthemselves, stating they must wait for
OL,9,Fa gas engineer to do it for them.
OL,11,FIn the evening, Cadent asks residents
OL,12,Fto reduce their electricity usage
OL,13,Fafter reports of some streets in Ratby
OL,14,Flosing power.
OL,16,FCadent stated: "If we have given you a
OL,17,Ffan heater, please DO NOT use other
OL,18,Fhigh usage electrical appliances, such
OL,19,Fas a washing machine, tumble dryer or
OL,20,Fhair straighteners at the same time.
