OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,F"This will over load the electricity
OL,7,Fnetwork and result in power cuts too."
OL,9,FCadent announced "restoring gas
OL,10,Fsupplies in Kirby Muxloe Zone 4, went
OL,11,Fwell yesterday and more than half of
OL,12,Fhomes are now back on gas."
OL,14,FThey added: "However, we have found
OL,15,Fsome water in certain areas in Zone 4,
OL,16,Fso we have had to go back to pumping
OL,17,Fwater out of the pipes, which has
OL,18,Fslowed progress slightly.
