OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,FGas engineers will start restoring gas
OL,7,Fto buildings in Zone 3 - and Cadent
OL,8,Fadded that "with some additional work,
OL,9,Fwe will be able to get some streets
OL,10,Fback on in a new zone - Zone 1a."
OL,12,FWater is continuing to be pumped out
OL,13,Fof gas pipes in Zones 1 and 2 - the
OL,14,Fgas company stated that
OL,15,F"realistically, we won't be able to
OL,16,Fget gas back into these pipes until
OL,17,FFriday and into the weekend."
