OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,FElectricity was restored to the
OL,7,Faffected street - but Cadent continues
OL,8,Fto warn people to "use electricity
OL,9,Fwisely", adding: "Don't use too many
OL,10,Felectrical appliances all at the same
OL,11,Ftime."
OL,13,F30,000 litres of water has since been
OL,14,Fpumped out of the gas pipes. Cadent
OL,15,FGas employee Richard Sansom said: "We
OL,16,Fnow know the full extent of the impact
OL,17,Fto our network, and we've got our arms
OL,18,Faround that.
