OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,F"We're actively today (Wednesday 31
OL,7,FJanuary) clearing water out of our
OL,8,Fnetwork and we're starting to put gas
OL,9,Fback on.
OL,11,F"We haven't got a full timescale yet
OL,12,Fof it as we don't know where the water
OL,13,Fhas settled precisely, but in the next
OL,14,Fday or so we'll have further
OL,15,Finformation to share with people."
OL,17,FAcross village halls in Ratby and
OL,18,FKirby Muxloe, Cadent employees and
OL,19,Fvolunteers handed out heaters,
OL,20,Fblankets, socks and supplies to help
OL,21,Fkeep locals warm during the crisis.
