OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,FCouncillor Ozzy O'Shea, from
OL,7,FLeicestershire County Council, said:
OL,8,F"We've got people here being given
OL,9,Fheaters, blankets, just to make sure
OL,10,Fthat they can carry on, because it
OL,11,Fcould be days before we get gas back
OL,12,Fin Ratby.
OL,14,F"So basically, I'm very proud of the
OL,15,Fcommunity, we have a fantastic
OL,16,Fcommunity spirit, we work hard, we
OL,17,Flook after each other, and people have
OL,18,Fbeen coming down to get stuff for
OL,19,Ftheir neighbours."
OL,21,FSaturday 3 February
