OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,F200 engineers and support teams are
OL,7,Fstill working in Kirby Muxloe and
OL,8,FRatby to restore gas to properties.
OL,10,FApproximately half of homes are still
OL,11,Fwithout gas, and Ratby Village Hall
OL,12,Fremains open for those needing hot
OL,13,Ffood, blankets and electric heaters.
OL,15,FGas in back in the pipes in Zones 1, 3
OL,16,Fand 4, meaning many homes will soon
OL,17,Fhave their gas restored.
OL,19,FHowever, there is still water in some
OL,20,Fof the pipes, and engineers are unsure
OL,21,Fhow long the issue will last.
