OL,3,CVillagers rally together after network
OL,4,C'incident' leaves homes without heating
OL,6,FRichard Sansom, the Cadent Network
OL,7,FDirector for the East Midlands told
OL,8,FITV News Central: "As we go down the
OL,9,Fhill to Kirby Muxloe we're finding
OL,10,Fmore and more water, although we think
OL,11,Fwe've found the worst impacted area
OL,12,Fwhich is Kirby Muxloe so things are
OL,13,Fever improving.
OL,15,F"In the next day or so we should have
OL,16,Fa good understanding of how long this
OL,17,Fis going to take to wrap up."
OL,19,FAffected residents have been told to
OL,20,Fexpect information about how to claim
OL,21,Fcompensation on Monday.
